snippet.title: Prompt Gallery | EP13 | Power Up Minute
snippet.description:
Discover how to access and use the M365 Copilot Prompt Gallery, including filtering prompts by task, agent, and saving your own for easy collaboration.

Learn quick tips to enhance productivity with Copilot in your Microsoft 365 tenant. Click the link below to join the Power Up cohort and be part of the growing community:
 
https://aka.ms/PowerUp_Ref_Min
 
And don't forget to connect with peers on the Power Up LinkedIn Group below:
 
https://aka.ms/PowerUpProgram/LI
 
#PowerUp #PowerUpMinute #Microsoft365 #Copilot #M365Copilot #ChatTools #ProductivityTips #Prompts #PromptGallery
